{
  "context": "Should we use RabbitMQ or Azure Service Bus for our new microservices event-driven architecture? We are building an e-commerce platform with order processing, inventory updates, and notification services. We expect around 5,000 messages per minute at peak and the team is split between Azure-native and cloud-agnostic preferences."
